content: The wilds of Ancient China can be a dangerous place, and you'll need every boost in power you can get. Luckily we have the locations of important collectibles to boost your power, your healing gourd, and even places to earn free skill points.

The wilds of Ancient China can be a dangerous place, and you'll need every boost in power you can get. Luckily we have the locations of important collectibles to boost your power, your healing gourd, and even places to earn free skill points.
